93
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,720
My sister and I would feed pigeons in the evening.

94
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,680
Not seagulls.

95
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,720
Back then,

96
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:51,860
