151
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,450
I was thinking at that time.

152
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:00,880
No matter what,

153
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,850
I had to investigate it myself.

154
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,560
That night,

