00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,080
I'll follow all your orders.

291
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,160
Tell me.

292
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:36,680
Does the law only protect victims?

293
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:41,880
What do you mean?

294
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,160
Go now.

295
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:47,420
I won't disappoint you again.

296
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:53,360
It doesn't matter if I'm disappointed.

297
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,200
He's the one

298
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:56,540
who's truly disappointed in you.

299
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,330
K is waiting for you.

300
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:22,800
Coming.

301
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,730
You're always so reliable.

302
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:29,520
All these years,

303
00:14:29,920 --> 00:14:31,650
you've never disappointed me.

304
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:34,520
You're too kind.

305
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,460
I'm just doing my best.

306
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,360
You asked me to come here.

307
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:47,420
Is there another assignment?

308
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:50,330
Don't always talk about assignments.

309
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:52,080
In your eyes,

310
00:14:52,400 --> 00:14:54,130
am I really that cold-hearted?

311
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:55,600
Not at all.

312
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:01,080
I called you back from China this time

313
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:04,960
because I want you to spend New Year with me.

314
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:09,200
Those who can chat with me about everyday matters,

315
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,360
besides those two,

316
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:12,740
there's only you left.

317
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:17,040
Drink slowly.

318
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:19,540
I just added hot water.

319
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:22,400
If you drink tea too hastily,

320
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:24,540
burning your tongue is a minor issue,

321
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:26,420
but if you swallow such hot water,

322
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:29,290
it could damage your internal organs.

323
00:15:32,160 --> 00:15:33,400
Indeed, some things

324
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:34,700
are better learned

325
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,720
from others

326
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:39,610
than through self-discovery.

327
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,200
Do you still remember

328
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:45,360
everything I taught you?

329
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,600
I wouldn't dare forget for a moment.

330
00:15:47,800 --> 00:15:50,860
I'm well aware of what Chi Xiao is doing on the mainland.

331
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:54,370
Whether it succeeds or fails, I'll make my own judgment.

332
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:57,640
But given your position,

333
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:01,490
there are some matters you should be involved in,

334
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:03,600
and others you should stay away from.

335
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:08,280
This is for the bigger picture.

336
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:11,540
Water has a boiling point.

337
00:16:11,800 --> 00:16:13,200
People have principles.

338
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:15,280
Don't cross the line.

339
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,000
I understand.

340
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:21,440
If you don't drink it soon,

341
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,440
it will get cold.

342
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:36,620
Almost.

343
00:18:01,360 --> 00:18:02,890
In the year I turned twelve.

344
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:05,120
What really happened?

345
00:18:11,520 --> 00:18:12,440
In this world,

346
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:14,840
it's all about who dares

347
00:18:14,840 --> 00:18:16,480
to go further than others.

348
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:20,040
But my parents,

349
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,640
they underestimated me.

350
00:18:24,040 --> 00:18:26,320
As long as I can catch the killer with my own hands,

351
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:27,720
I'm willing to die for it.

352
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:32,320
Ready?

353
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,360
Let's try.

354
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:51,080
What happened to your hand?

355
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:53,520
I've fantasized countless times

356
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,650
about dying together with him.

357
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:57,700
Trying to save my life now,

358
00:18:57,800 --> 00:18:59,060
isn't it a bit too late?

359
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:02,400
The victim's body contains nerve-paralyzing drugs.

360
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:04,060
If my speculation is correct,

361
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,720
this should be a premeditated murder.
